<pb ed="T" id="T02.0109.0503b" n="0503b"/>
<lb n="0503b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><head type="no">No. 109 [No. 99(379), No. 110]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0503b02"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0503013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0503013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0503013"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>轉法輪經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0503b03"/>
<lb n="0503b04"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0503014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後漢安息三藏＝後漢【宋】【元】，後漢安息國三藏法師【元】</note><note n="0503014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後漢安息三藏＝後漢【宋】，<todo type="i"/>後漢安息三藏＝後漢【元】，＝後漢安息國三藏法師【元】</note><app n="0503014"><lem>後漢安息三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">後漢</rdg></app>安世高譯</byline>
<lb n="0503b05"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在波羅<note n="0503015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00178;＝柰【明】</note><app n="0503015"><lem>&CB00178;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">柰</rdg></app>國鹿野樹下坐。時
<lb n="0503b06"/>有千比丘諸天神。皆大會<note n="0503016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">側＝畟【元】【明】</note><app n="0503016"><lem>側</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">畟</rdg></app>塞空中。於是有
<lb n="0503b07"/>自然法輪。飛來當佛前轉。佛以手撫輪曰。
<lb n="0503b08"/><note n="0503017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止＝上【明】</note><app n="0503017"><lem>止</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上</rdg></app>往者吾從無數劫來。為名色轉<note n="0503018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝更【三】</note><note n="0503018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝更【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503018"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">更</rdg></app>苦無
<lb n="0503b09"/>量。今者癡愛之意已止。漏結之情已解。諸
<lb n="0503b10"/>根已定生死已斷。不復轉於五道也。輪即
<lb n="0503b11"/><note n="0503019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止＝上【元】</note><app n="0503019"><lem>止</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">上</rdg></app>。於是佛告諸比丘。世間有二事墮邊行。
<lb n="0503b12"/>行道弟子捨家者。終身不當與從事。何等二。
<lb n="0503b13"/>一為念在貪欲無清淨志。二為<note n="0503020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猗＝倚【明】</note><app n="0503020"><lem>猗</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">倚</rdg></app>著<note n="0503021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔身〕－【三】</note><note n="0503021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔身〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503021"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>愛
<lb n="0503b14"/>不能精進。是故退邊行。不得值佛道德<note n="0503022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝真【三】</note><note n="0503022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具＝真【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503022"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app>
<lb n="0503b15"/>人。若此比丘不念貪欲著身愛行。可得受中。
<lb n="0503b16"/>如來最正覺得眼得慧。從兩邊度自致泥洹。
<lb n="0503b17"/>何謂受中。謂受八直之道。一曰正見。二曰
<lb n="0503b18"/>正思。三曰正言。四曰正行。五曰正命。六曰
<lb n="0503b19"/>正治。七曰正<note n="0503023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝念【三】</note><note n="0503023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志＝念【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503023"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>。八曰正定。若諸比丘本<note n="0503024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">末＝未【元】【明】</note><app n="0503024"><lem>末</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0503b20"/>聞道。當已知甚苦為真諦。已一心受眼受禪
<lb n="0503b21"/>思受慧見覺所念令意解。當知甚苦<note n="0503025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">集</rdg></app>盡為
<lb n="0503b22"/>真諦。已受眼觀禪思慧見覺所念令意解。如
<lb n="0503b23"/>是盡真諦。何謂為苦。謂生老苦病苦憂悲惱
<lb n="0503b24"/>苦怨憎會苦所愛別苦求不得苦。要從五陰
<lb n="0503b25"/>受盛為苦。何謂苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>。謂從愛故而令復有樂
<lb n="0503b26"/>性。不離在在貪&CB00540;。欲愛色愛不色之愛。是
<lb n="0503b27"/><app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>為苦。何謂苦盡。謂覺從愛復有所樂。婬
<lb n="0503b28"/>念不<note n="0503026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝愛【三】</note><note n="0503026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝愛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503026"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">愛</rdg></app>。不念無餘無婬。捨之無復禪。如是
<lb n="0503b29"/>為<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡。何謂苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡欲受道。謂受行八直
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0109.0503c" n="0503c"/>
<lb n="0503c01"/>道。正見正思正言正行正命正治正志正定。
<lb n="0503c02"/>是為苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡受道真諦也</p>
<lb n="0503c03"/><p>又是比丘苦為真諦。苦由<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>為真諦。苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>
<lb n="0503c04"/>盡為真諦。苦<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>盡欲受道為真諦。若本在昔
<lb n="0503c05"/>未聞是法者。當受眼觀禪行受慧見受覺念
<lb n="0503c06"/>令意得解。若令在斯未聞是四諦法者。當受
<lb n="0503c07"/>道眼受禪思受慧覺令意<note n="0503027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝得【三】</note><note n="0503027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝得【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503027"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>解。若諸在彼不
<lb n="0503c08"/>得聞是四諦法者。亦當受眼受禪受慧受覺
<lb n="0503c09"/>令意得解。是為四諦三轉合十二事。知而未
<lb n="0503c10"/>淨者吾不與也。一切世間諸天人民若梵若
<lb n="0503c11"/>魔沙門梵志。自知證已受行戒定慧解<note n="0503028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝受【明】</note><app n="0503028"><lem>度</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0503c12"/>見成。是為四極。是生後不復有。長離世間無
<lb n="0503c13"/>復憂患。佛說是時。賢者阿若拘鄰等及八
<lb n="0503c14"/><note n="0503029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">千＝十【三】</note><note n="0503029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">千＝十【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503029"><lem>千</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">十</rdg></app>&CB00108;天。皆遠塵離垢諸法眼生。其千比丘
<lb n="0503c15"/>漏盡意解皆得<note n="0503030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【三】</note><note n="0503030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔阿〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503030"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>羅漢。及上諸<app type="＊" source="0503025"><lem>習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>法應當
<lb n="0503c16"/>盡者一切皆轉。眾祐法輪聲三轉。諸天世間
<lb n="0503c17"/>在法地者莫不遍聞。至<note n="0503031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝於【明】</note><app n="0503031"><lem>于</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>第一四天王忉
<lb n="0503c18"/>利天<note n="0503032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">焰＋（摩）【三】</note><note n="0503032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">焰＋（摩）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0503032"><lem>焰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">焰摩</rdg></app>天兜術天不驕樂天化應聲天。至諸
<lb n="0503c19"/>梵界須臾遍聞。爾時佛界三千日月萬二千
<lb n="0503c20"/>天地皆大震動。是為佛眾祐。始於波羅<note n="0503033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00178;＝捺【元】，柰【明】</note><note n="0503033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00178;＝捺【元】，＝柰【明】</note><app n="0503033"><lem>&CB00178;</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">捺</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">柰</rdg></app>以
<lb n="0503c21"/>無上法輪轉未轉者。照無數度諸天人從是
<lb n="0503c22"/>得道。佛說是已。皆大歡喜</p>
<lb n="0503c23"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><app type="＊" source="0503013"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>轉法輪經</jhead></juan></div1>
